## Database & Prisma

- All DB access must go through Prisma Client; no raw SQL unless unavoidable
- Use Prisma transactions for multi-step operations
- All models defined in `schema.prisma`; keep migrations versioned
- Always use `select` to avoid over-fetching fields
- DB query functions live in `lib/db/[feature].ts`
- Never call Prisma directly from components or Server Actions — go through `lib/db/`

## Patterns
\`\`\`ts
// ✅ Good
const user = await prisma.user.findUnique({
  where: { id },
  select: { id: true, name: true, email: true },
})

// ❌ Bad - over-fetching
const user = await prisma.user.findUnique({ where: { id } })
\`\`\`